<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/coronavirus-shows-us-what-our-future-could-look-like-during-climate-crisis/">Coronavirus Shows Us What Our Future Could Look Like During Climate Crisis</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">COVID-19, like climate, isn’t just about a singular crisis &#8212; it&#8217;s about multiple crises unfolding all at once.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/sharon-zhang/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Sharon Zhang</a></span>, </dd>
